If you use the {{gg}} keyboard shortcut to open the Administration Quick Search dialog, search results can't be middle-clicked to open a new tab. Also, you can't right-click the items and choose "Open in a new tab."

AQS is one of the most useful keyboard shortcuts for admins, and having multiple tabs open can be extremely useful for some configuration issues. Any chance we could make those links new tab friendly?
